quran[25]{c,v,t}:
  21,51,"Re ile Ra neha Abrahama kholo e nepahetseng khale, Re bile hlokolosi ka eena"
  21,52,"Hopola mohla a reng ho ntata’e le ho batho ba habo: “Ke ling lits’oants’o tsena tseo le li rapelang?”"
  21,53,"Ba re: “Re fumane bo-ntata rona ba li khumamela.”"
  21,54,"Abrahama a re: “Ruri lona le bo-ntata lona le bile phosong e hlakileng.”"
  21,55,"Ba re: “Joale, uena u re tliselitse ‘nete, kapa u e mong oa ba soasoang?”"
  21,56,"Abrahama a re: “Che, Mong`a lona ke Mong`a maholimo le lefats’e, Ea A hlotseng; le ‘na ke paki ea seo"
  21,57,"Ka Allah, ke na le leano ka melingoana ena ea lona, hoba le tsamae, le furalle"
  21,58,"Eaba o e khaola likotoana kaofela, a siea se seholo har’a tsona, hore ba tle ba se botse lipotso"
  21,59,"Ba re: “Ke mang ea thuileng melingoana ea rona tje? Ruri! E tlameha e le e mong oa baetsa-libe.”"
  21,60,"Ba re: “Re utloile mohlankana a buoa ka eona: ea bitsoang Abrahama.”"
  21,61,"Ba re: “mo tliseng ponts’eng ea batho, hore ba tle ba fane ka bopaki.”"
  21,62,"Ba re: “Abrahama! Na ke uena ea entseng melingoana ea rona ka tsela e tje?”"
  21,63,"Abrahama a re: “Che se entsoe-, ke ena e kholo. Li botseng haeba li tseba ho bua.”"
  21,64,"Ba qamaka koana le koana, ba re: “Ruri ke rona ba phoso.”"
  21,65,"Ba hlajoa ke lihlong, ba re: “Ruri! U tseba hantle hore lits’oants’so tsena ha li tsebe ho buoa.”"
  21,66,"Abrahama a re: “Joale le khumamela lintho tse ke keng tsa le thusa ka letho, leha e le hona ho le hlahisetsa kotsi kathoko ho Allah"
  21,67,“Masoabi a be ho lona le lintho tsohle tseo le li rapelang ntle ho Allah! Ha le na kelello na?”
  21,68,"Ba re: “Mo cheseng, le sireletse melingoana ea lona haeba le ka khona.”"
  21,69,"Re Re: “Mollo! Bata, o be sets’abelo ho Abrahama!”"
  21,70,"Eaba ba etsa sefi khahlanong le eena: empa Ra ba etsa ba lahlehetsoeng ka ho fetisisa"
  21,71,"Re ile Ra mo pholosa le Lota, Ra ba lebisa naheng eo Re e hlonolofalitseng molemong oa lichaba tsohle"
  21,72,"Ra mo sitsa ka Isaaka, le Jakobo e le mpho ea tlatsetso. Ra ba apesa ka toka e mong le e mong oa bona"
  21,73,"Ra ba etsa Baetapele ba tataisang ka Taelo ea Rona, Ra ba susumelitsa ho etsa liketso tse lokileng, le ho phethahatsa lithapelo tsa mehla le ho fana ka linyehelo; ba re sebeletsa kamehla"
  21,74,"Lota le eena Re ile Ra mo neha Kahlolo le Tsebo, Ra mo pholosa har›a motse o neng o etsa manyala. Ruri! E ne e le batho ba oetseng sebeng le bona bojela-thoko"
  21,75,Ra mo atametsa haufi le Mohau oa Rona. Hobane e ne e le e mong oa ba lokileng